| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5436 — Recovery Inhibition (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c38ab2b6-6507-5fde-a4b8-8f1ebcd4c987"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
